description: This common Sakura purrs with a rating of 2, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 6, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [6 Votes, Common]
